# Syslog Viewer Version 1.0
# by Trevor Manternach (trevormanternach.com)
#
# Features of this version include:
#  - Live updating
#  - Search: The search is limited to 300 items by default. It will return the 300 newest matches.
#  - Highlight to search: Highlighting (almost) any text on the page will automatically paste the text into the search box. Pressing Enter will show the search results.
#
